Natural gas consumption¶

"Dataset covers six whole years from 2013 to 2019 of natural gas consumption in Prague. All data features are available at an hourly frequency. The whole dataset is composed of 52,584 data points. These data points were assembled from three main components.

The second component includes weather variables. We have used data from the Prague LKPR airport weather station. Airports are required to periodically issue METAR (aerodrome routine meteorological report) information. Those reports are archived and preserved for a long time."

Correlation¶

In [6]:
df.loc[df['visibility'] != '10.0 and more', 'visibility'] = 0
df.loc[df['visibility'] == '10.0 and more', 'visibility'] = 1

t = 0.2
df_corr = df[['temperature', 'pressure', 'humidity', 'wind_speed', 'visibility', 'price', 'visibility', 'consumption']].copy()
corr = df_corr.corr()

matrix = np.triu(corr)
plt.figure(figsize = (16, 10))

sns.heatmap(corr[(corr >= t) | (corr <= -t)], mask = matrix, cmap = pal, vmax = 1.0, vmin = -1.0, annot = True, annot_kws = {"size": 8}, square = True);

*Zobrazeny jsou pouze korelace nad hodnotou 0,2 bez horn poloviny a diagonly.

  • spoteba zemnho plynu je ve velk zporn korelaci s teplotou
  • spoteba zemnho plynu je ve mal a stedn kladn korelaci s vlhkost vzduchu
  • spoteba zemnho plynu je ve velmi mal korelaci s cenou
  • sloupec tlaku vzduchu nen v korelaci s dnm numerickm sloupcem datasetu

Resid (anomaly detection)¶

In [17]:
lower = r.mean() - 3 * r.std()
upper = r.mean() + 3 * r.std()

plt.figure(figsize = (16, 6))
plt.plot(r)
plt.axhline(y = lower, color = 'r', linestyle = '--')
plt.axhline(y = upper, color = 'r', linestyle = '--')
plt.xlim([datetime(2013, 1, 1), datetime(2019, 6, 30)])
plt.show()
In [18]:
anomalies = df_new[(r < lower) | (r > upper)]

plt.figure(figsize = (16, 6))
plt.scatter(anomalies.index, anomalies.consumption, color = 'r', linewidth=0, zorder=2, s = 8)
plt.plot(df_new, zorder=1)
plt.show()

Conclusion¶

  • Spoteba plynu je men v nonch hodinch a o vkendu.
  • Sloupce teploty, vlhkosti vzduchu a ceny jsou v urit me v linern korelaci se spotebou a proto mohou bt zajmav pi pedpovdi.
  • asov ada postrd trend a cyklinost, ale obsahuje silnou seznn sloku.
  • V ad byly nalezeny ti vznamn anomlie a vechny le v prvn polovin roku.
